properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS - BANKSTOWN Stacey Street between Stanley Street/Salvia Ave AND Macauley Avenue
properties.otherAdvice:
Work is taking place to construct a third northbound lane on Stacey St.

1 of 3 southbound lanes is currently closed.

  • Northbound carriageway: lane 1 will be closed; lane 2 will remain open and northbound traffic will also use a contained southbound lane under contra flow conditions

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS - JENOLAN Jenolan Caves Road between Five Mile AND Caves House
properties.otherAdvice:
Two Mile section of Jenolan Caves Rd is now open.

  • Access/egress strictly via the Two Mile, which requires travel through Oberon and via Edith Rd.
  • Maximum size of vehicle that can travel up and down Two Mile is a 12-seater bus.
  • Two Mile is NOT suitable for caravans and/or trailers.
  • Traffic control crews will remain in place 24 hours a day at closure points north of Jenolan Caves (Five Mile).

NOTE: Road closure lines provided by Google Maps may not be up to date.
